=======
Roadmap
=======

0.5.x
=====

Templates for:
* Ubuntu
* Slack
* Busybox

First functional roles for:
* Debian Secure
* Web Server
* LDAP Server

0.6.x
=====

* more functional roles
* Converting openvz-templates > LXC containers
* X.org tty out for a Container

0.7.x
=====

* LXC on ARM!
* android for LXC
* firefox-OS for LXC
